Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}焰之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}世事无常 谁能预料得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\an8}骑兵队 右翼展开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}解放拼写 冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在几个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和凛还只是两个随处可见的普通高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}过着平凡安稳 却也还算充足的小日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却变成这番模样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}落…落叶之魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟然知道我的名讳 真让你说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给你个小奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你…你竟然…怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讲真 越来越觉得自己这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也太开挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}——————OP———————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:31.34,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}自身所感 自身所见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.34,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}一切都在崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:41.60,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}高楼大厦也毫无征兆地倒塌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:51.81,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}浓郁的色彩亦悄然剥落 唯有框架空洞残留
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:55.82,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}我们的真实在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:02:02.57,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}失去象征 开始迷茫的大众啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:07.16,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}相信你自己的认知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:10.29,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}我不再需要真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.63,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}正视这疯狂的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:17.17,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}不要被他人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:20.47,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}我不再需要真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:25.47,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}坦然走向骚然和噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:44.58,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}自身所感 自身所见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:48.16,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}自身所感
