Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:54.50,EP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(1430,1050)}{\blur2}第1话 来自异世界的「迷途人」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天放了学还要练网球?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}毕竟大赛快开始了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样啊 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一 你真的不打算加入个社团什么的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就算了 嫌麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从小到大 你唯一值得称道的就是运动神经还算发达了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怀才不用 说的就是你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么叫唯一的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于完成了是吗 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此总算不负父王所托…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么会…怎么会找到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可以…不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}殿…殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 骑车不长眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是…什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这不就跟游戏似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛 凛你先出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听我的 快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快醒醒啊 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢天谢地 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个…你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有没有觉得哪里痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我虽然没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可这里是哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之咱们得先找个有人烟的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}联系一下家里人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这年头你见过哪个乡下没信号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里不就是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说 这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真觉得还是咱们原来住的那个世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个类似魔法阵的东西你也见到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那可不是什么CG一类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我感觉到一种很特别的…类似某种力量的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也觉得又不是在玩游戏 也太玄乎了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可这里果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我求你别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那种事怎么可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那不是咱们所熟知的马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它不会是想将咱们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还能跑吗 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跑远点 能离我多远就离我多远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找个地方躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就趁机逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是…快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么一来你不就死定了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才要你跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一定要逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死在这里的人 一个就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就让身为青梅竹马的我展现一下男子风范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 来追我呀 臭马
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是…我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟挠痒痒似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的饵料是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来呀 来追我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很好 我还怕你不生气呢 臭混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赶紧来追我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这身大块头是装饰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}旋风斩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚刚骂的真是大快人心啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黑曜马的皮就是厚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来选择用秘银箭是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黑曜马…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它头上的角
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是黑曜石的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因此得名黑曜马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在这一带是最强的魔物了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明明是匹马却会喷火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且还是肉食动物 会吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的有够棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 很值钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要开烤了 离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}美丽的小姐这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火焰长矛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不愧是梅西莉亚 下手还是这么狠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拉克鲁达 记得把角收好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}力气活儿不应该交给布拉达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}近期内都不用担心没口粮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这一刻 我终于确信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}魔物 秘银箭还有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看似像是RPG的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可实际却是如假包换的真实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有就是 因缘际会之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们被那个魔法阵召唤到了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或许感觉这种设定脑洞太大不真实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但唯有一点可以确定 那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和凛哪怕不惜一切代价 也要在这个世界活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:11:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话说你们两个是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们不是这一带的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连黑曜马都不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}穿着也很奇异
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然做工精良 款式也好看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就别瞎打听了 拉克鲁达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁还没有个小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不想说的话不必勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过出门在外手无寸铁就太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尤其最近这附近魔物袭击事件频发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过对于我们这些冒险者来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能多一些工作倒是求之不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冒险者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前往城镇的运货马车时有遇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不断有人丧生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最近这段时间事态越发严峻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚刚是提到城镇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是指阿兹派亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}承了你们的救命之恩还敢提要求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或许是有些厚颜无耻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别客气 带你们去当然没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也就罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}像小凛这样楚楚可人的妙龄少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么好将手无缚鸡之力的她留在这荒郊野岭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}救人于水火也是冒险者的职责之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过相应的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在天亮前 你可得跟人家妹子和好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从刚才起就这样 你在气什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁说我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别骗我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们俩可是从小一起长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一生气就会变得沉默寡言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果是我的做法惹你生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我跟你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我到底是错在哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不许你再做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那种事是哪种事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个人赴死什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当时也是形势所迫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就因为你是男的? 少耍帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要丢下我一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从今往后不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我都不会再丢下你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一定与你齐心协力 共渡难关
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 那就这么说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老规矩 和好的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}结果他就掉到洞里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里就是阿茲派亚城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是中心街
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尽管不及王城惠内菲克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过也挺热闹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然是边境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但也是埃里斯汀魔法王国的要冲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里也是我们的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冒险者公会就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很显眼 一眼就能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过你们真要当冒险者?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先声明 这个职业是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 我们都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即便如此 我们总得有份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们想靠自己的双手生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先从我们能做的做起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一点一点积蓄力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的很感谢诸位的关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这份恩情我们永世不忘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}饯别礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}够你们生活一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想当冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必要的装备也不能少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用客气 我们还有它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三位…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们住在一个叫「米斯里鲁」的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遇到什么麻烦尽管来找我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有缘再见 小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}祝你们好运
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那咱们…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来了两个生面孔呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是来登记成为冒险者的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}两位都要登记吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}种族是人族?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人族?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是人的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种游戏设定似的东西不是你的专长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太像游戏了 惊到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}契约详情请看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是哪国文字 看不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「冒险者公会指南」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看懂了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过仔细一想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们跟这个世界的人都能正常交流的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最后一项
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请二位做一下魔力的适应性检测
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要成为冒险者 魔力是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有魔力的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很遗憾 没有办法进行登记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这没什么复杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只需轻轻触碰面前的水晶球即可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我先试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就知道没这么便宜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凛小姐 您到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一先生 该不会您也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不太明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请将手放在水晶球上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎 怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二…二位请在这里稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们搞出大新闻了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会长亲自接见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连金之剑士都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有问题的就是你们二位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是公会会长 杰拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公会会长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是大人物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很不巧 目前无法让二位在这里进行冒险者登记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无法登记…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那也无法接委托咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}缪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二位需要跟随她到另一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去获取给予你们的箴言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都不说明情况就让我们跟着走也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不去就无法成为冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么 我就这么不可信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不许看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}疼 指甲…指甲抠到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 怎么穿成这样就出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想怎么穿还用经过别人同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贵客临门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是这里的主人 蕾米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欢迎你们 少年少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公会的计测器也测试不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以会长只得拜托蕾米娅小姐帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在需要我们做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来试试这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是测定魔力量和魔力强度的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}魔力量是测量对象所能持有的魔力容量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}魔力强度…就字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然跟RPG很像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}RPG?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没听说过呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}简而言之 就是看看你们这两个容器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能装多么烈的酒 装多少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是用来了解它的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}显示其人的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}浮现出文字了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蕾米娅小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这真是惊到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问有什么不对的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}魔力量该不会是零吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}魔力量是零? 你可真能想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会吧 这个数值…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那结论呢? 我们到底能不能成为冒险者?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只不过 太一 凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从今天起 你们就是我的徒弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么说来已经成功干扰到召唤术了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是 但是由于施术者力量强大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尽管出现错乱 但术式依旧发动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「迷途人」的搜查进行的如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经在所有城池布下天罗地网
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}近几日应当就能收到反馈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那位大人也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好生努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来自异世界的「迷途人」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}——————ED———————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:19.79,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}无论哭脸还是笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:24.13,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}我明明全都见过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:29.09,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}可唯有最棒的感情无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:34.06,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}不禁询问自己的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.14,0:22:42.86,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}你的魔法还无法解开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:51.82,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}小小的感情 开始增长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:23:02.67,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}不曾知晓的感情 就藏在内心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:11.72,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}就像温柔的风吹拂 只要两人同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:22.10,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}当有你陪伴的日常 逐渐明白它的宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:29.53,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}这如水面荡起一圈圈波纹的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:34.24,OPED,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(200,200)}总有一天 会意识到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}——————ED———————
